1
00:01:43,666 --> 00:01:45,791
[sirens]

2
00:01:47,416 --> 00:01:49,500
[MAN ON POLICE COM] We’ve set up
a barricade around the building

3
00:01:49,583 --> 00:01:51,458
and several blocks out.

4
00:01:51,541 --> 00:01:54,250
-[cameras shutters clicking]
-No suspects identified yet.

5
00:01:54,333 --> 00:01:57,041
We’re continuing
our investigation at this time.

6
00:01:57,125 --> 00:01:58,166
Over.

7
00:02:03,291 --> 00:02:06,333
-[footsteps]
-[fast running breaths]

8
00:02:10,083 --> 00:02:12,000
[squealing]

9
00:02:12,083 --> 00:02:13,583
What’s that guys deal?

10
00:02:13,666 --> 00:02:14,916
Who knows?

11
00:02:16,416 --> 00:02:18,166
[SUIGIN]
No. It’s a lie!

12
00:02:18,250 --> 00:02:19,916
[RANSHOU]
I’m afraid not.

13
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:22,916
Yuuki Riku, vice president
of the God Grave Tech Company,

14
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:25,333
was murdered last night
in his office.

15
00:02:27,208 --> 00:02:28,375
[SUIGIN]
But he’s...

16
00:02:28,458 --> 00:02:30,541
[RANSHOU]
Yeah. Rei Riku’s father.

17
00:02:31,916 --> 00:02:33,291
[gasping]

18
00:02:34,958 --> 00:02:36,250
[SUIGIN]
No.

19
00:02:37,458 --> 00:02:39,666
[fast running breaths]

20
00:02:39,750 --> 00:02:40,916
[SUIGIN]
Rei!

21
00:02:47,458 --> 00:02:49,500
[shimmering]

22
00:02:57,583 --> 00:02:59,541
[MAKI]
Sorry, Rei already left.

23
00:02:59,625 --> 00:03:02,375
[breathing heavily]

24
00:03:02,458 --> 00:03:04,333
Okay, do you know
where she went?

25
00:03:04,416 --> 00:03:05,916
Apparently there’s
a lot of paperwork

26
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:07,708
for the funeral arrangements.

27
00:03:07,791 --> 00:03:10,916
So, people from
the company took her.

28
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,958
She said she’ll be gone
for a while.

29
00:03:15,125 --> 00:03:17,208
I feel awful for her.

30
00:03:17,291 --> 00:03:19,166
She loved her dad
more than anything.

31
00:03:22,250 --> 00:03:23,833
[SUIGIN]
Poor Rei.

32
00:03:34,083 --> 00:03:36,250
[FEMALE FOREMAN 1]
Such a tragedy.

33
00:03:36,333 --> 00:03:37,500
[FEMALE FOREMAN 2]
To think her only

34
00:03:37,583 --> 00:03:40,166
living relative would
end up like that.

35
00:03:40,250 --> 00:03:41,291
[FEMALE FOREMAN 1]
I heard he left behind

36
00:03:41,375 --> 00:03:43,458
an enormous amount of debt, too.

37
00:03:43,541 --> 00:03:44,791
Poor little thing.

38
00:03:44,875 --> 00:03:46,791
She’s got a tough road
ahead of her.

39
00:03:55,041 --> 00:03:56,750
[LING]
My friend, Yuuki

40
00:03:56,833 --> 00:03:58,041
dedicated his life

41
00:03:58,125 --> 00:04:00,458
to creating the best games
in the world.

42
00:04:00,541 --> 00:04:03,416
He sacrificed
his own happiness

43
00:04:03,500 --> 00:04:06,416
so we could enjoy
the fruits of his labor.

44
00:04:06,500 --> 00:04:07,750
Even now,

45
00:04:07,833 --> 00:04:10,083
I can’t believe
a light as bright as his

46
00:04:10,166 --> 00:04:13,125
was snuffed out
so early, and so cruelly.

47
00:04:14,083 --> 00:04:15,458
Whatever the reason,

48
00:04:15,541 --> 00:04:18,000
I can’t begin to imagine
what he could have done

49
00:04:18,083 --> 00:04:19,875
to deserve such an end.

50
00:04:19,958 --> 00:04:22,000
I vow that
the God Grave Tech company

51
00:04:22,083 --> 00:04:24,250
will work around the clock
with law enforcement

52
00:04:24,333 --> 00:04:27,083
to find the culprit
of this reprehensible crime,

53
00:04:27,166 --> 00:04:30,125
and prosecute them to
the fullest extent of the law.

54
00:04:30,208 --> 00:04:34,000
And to all our loyal fans,
I make this solemn promise:

55
00:04:34,083 --> 00:04:37,625
we will do everything we can
to make sure his final game,

56
00:04:37,708 --> 00:04:40,208
Grave Buster,
is a world-wide success

57
00:04:40,291 --> 00:04:42,416
that can be enjoyed
for years to come.

58
00:04:52,458 --> 00:04:53,916
[gasps]

59
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:56,541
Hey. Hold on.

60
00:04:58,166 --> 00:05:00,208
Did I know him?

61
00:05:00,291 --> 00:05:01,416
How?

62
00:05:11,083 --> 00:05:13,333
[birds chirping]

63
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:18,458
[REI] Sorry for asking you
to come here.

64
00:05:18,541 --> 00:05:20,666
I’m sure you had
better things to do.

65
00:05:20,750 --> 00:05:21,708
You’re so busy.

66
00:05:21,791 --> 00:05:24,333
Oh, please. It's no trouble...

67
00:05:24,416 --> 00:05:25,875
at all.

68
00:05:27,291 --> 00:05:30,291
Well, uh... I’m so sorry.

69
00:05:30,375 --> 00:05:33,375
[REI]
Thank you. I’m fine now, really.

70
00:05:33,458 --> 00:05:35,708
More importantly,

71
00:05:35,791 --> 00:05:39,166
there’s something very special
that I’d like you have.

72
00:05:41,375 --> 00:05:42,625
[SUIGIN]
For me?

73
00:05:46,291 --> 00:05:48,541
[YUUKI]
In the event of my death,

74
00:05:48,625 --> 00:05:51,000
please give this to Suigin Riku.

75
00:05:51,083 --> 00:05:52,958
[SUIGIN]
It’s from your dad?

76
00:05:57,208 --> 00:05:59,708
Hold on. Isn’t this...?

77
00:05:59,791 --> 00:06:01,375
Yes, a Seabay.

78
00:06:01,458 --> 00:06:04,333
He created this console
to play Grave Buster.

79
00:06:04,416 --> 00:06:06,625
There’s never been
anything like it before.

80
00:06:07,916 --> 00:06:09,375
[gasps]

81
00:06:09,458 --> 00:06:12,125
Okay. Why did he want
me to have it?

82
00:06:16,958 --> 00:06:18,791
[FEMALE GAME VOICE]
User identification commencing.

83
00:06:21,500 --> 00:06:22,625
[shimmering]

84
00:06:29,125 --> 00:06:34,083
Username: Suigin Riku.
Identification complete.

85
00:06:34,166 --> 00:06:35,500
System starting.

86
00:06:36,458 --> 00:06:38,291
I’m confused.

87
00:06:38,375 --> 00:06:40,041
That makes two of us.

88
00:06:41,041 --> 00:06:42,375
[BOTH sigh]

89
00:06:44,041 --> 00:06:46,166
[gate clattering]

90
00:06:48,166 --> 00:06:52,041
[SUIGIN] Wait. I still don’t get
why he left this for me.

91
00:06:52,125 --> 00:06:53,333
[REI]
Me either.

92
00:06:55,625 --> 00:06:58,333
I didn’t really know my dad.

93
00:06:58,416 --> 00:07:00,791
In fact, I’m not
his biological daughter.

94
00:07:00,875 --> 00:07:01,708
[gasps]

95
00:07:01,791 --> 00:07:03,958
But, how is that...?

96
00:07:04,041 --> 00:07:07,000
I was really young,
so I don’t remember.

97
00:07:07,083 --> 00:07:09,791
All I know is he took me in
when I was a little girl.

98
00:07:10,791 --> 00:07:12,083
We were close.

99
00:07:12,166 --> 00:07:14,250
But, still,
he never told me about it.

100
00:07:15,583 --> 00:07:18,375
I’m sorry, Suigin.
I’ve made things awkward.

101
00:07:18,458 --> 00:07:20,416
No, not at all!
It’s totally fine!

102
00:07:20,500 --> 00:07:21,458
[knocking]

103
00:07:21,541 --> 00:07:22,708
[SECRETARY]
Miss Riku?

104
00:07:22,791 --> 00:07:23,708
Yes?

105
00:07:25,166 --> 00:07:27,000
Sorry, but you have
a guest outside.

106
00:07:27,083 --> 00:07:29,583
Oh! Thanks, I’ll be right out.

107
00:07:29,666 --> 00:07:31,166
Do you mind waiting for a bit?

108
00:07:31,250 --> 00:07:32,416
[SUIGIN]
Not at all.

109
00:07:33,916 --> 00:07:35,125
[grunts]

110
00:07:36,083 --> 00:07:37,000
[sighs]

111
00:07:40,416 --> 00:07:41,625
Right this way, miss.

112
00:07:44,500 --> 00:07:46,000
[MAN]
Hello.

113
00:07:46,083 --> 00:07:49,375
Didn't know Yuuki Riku’s
daughter was such a babe.

114
00:07:49,458 --> 00:07:51,333
[evil chuckling]

115
00:07:54,416 --> 00:07:55,458
[sighs]

116
00:07:57,416 --> 00:08:01,041
[shimmering]

117
00:08:01,125 --> 00:08:03,000
[FEMALE GAME VOICE]
Welcome to Grave Buster!

118
00:08:03,083 --> 00:08:04,708
What the...?

119
00:08:04,791 --> 00:08:05,958
[FEMALE GAME VOICE]
Your current saved wealth

120
00:08:06,041 --> 00:08:07,291
is displayed here.

121
00:08:07,375 --> 00:08:08,375
Observe.

122
00:08:08,458 --> 00:08:09,250
[shimmer]

123
00:08:09,333 --> 00:08:10,708
My what now?

124
00:08:10,791 --> 00:08:13,041
[beeping]

125
00:08:16,625 --> 00:08:17,708
[ching]

126
00:08:17,791 --> 00:08:20,625
One, ten, hundred, thousand.

127
00:08:20,708 --> 00:08:21,500
[exclaims]

128
00:08:21,583 --> 00:08:26,000
Ten? Ten billion?

129
00:08:26,083 --> 00:08:27,250
No way.

130
00:08:27,333 --> 00:08:29,833
This has gotta be
some kinda glitch.

131
00:08:29,916 --> 00:08:31,125
[shimmer]

132
00:08:31,208 --> 00:08:32,375
[YUUKI]
Ahem.

133
00:08:32,458 --> 00:08:34,208
[yells]

134
00:08:36,916 --> 00:08:39,958
[YUUKI]
Ah, testing, testing.

135
00:08:40,041 --> 00:08:40,958
[grunts]

136
00:08:41,041 --> 00:08:44,500
Suigin, I hope this message

137
00:08:44,583 --> 00:08:45,875
finds you well, my boy.

138
00:08:45,958 --> 00:08:46,958
[SUIGIN]
Huh?

139
00:08:47,041 --> 00:08:48,916
[YUUKI]
My name's Yuuki Riku.

140
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:53,333
I raised Rei as my own,
but I’m also your grandfather.

141
00:08:54,375 --> 00:08:58,583
Although, it’s been so long,
I doubt you even remember me.

142
00:08:58,666 --> 00:09:01,708
Grandfather? Really?

143
00:09:01,791 --> 00:09:04,166
[whooshing]

144
00:09:11,458 --> 00:09:12,958
[ELLE]
Mission complete.

145
00:09:13,041 --> 00:09:15,250
All the countermeasures
are in place.

146
00:09:15,333 --> 00:09:17,291
[LING]
I see. Well done.

147
00:09:17,375 --> 00:09:19,500
[ELLE]
Unfortunately, he ate a bullet

148
00:09:19,583 --> 00:09:21,541
before telling me
how to open the tomb.

149
00:09:21,625 --> 00:09:23,166
[LING]
It can’t be helped.

150
00:09:23,250 --> 00:09:25,416
We’ll just have to sort
through his estate

151
00:09:25,500 --> 00:09:27,625
piece by piece.

152
00:09:27,708 --> 00:09:30,291
[BASHIDA] There’s no need
to worry about that.

153
00:09:30,375 --> 00:09:32,208
All of his assets
have been eliminated,

154
00:09:32,291 --> 00:09:35,333
and his fake credit
has been sent off to collectors.

155
00:09:35,416 --> 00:09:37,666
You know how vicious
they can be.

156
00:09:37,750 --> 00:09:41,208
Such is the fate of all
who go against Precious.

157
00:09:41,291 --> 00:09:45,500
Death and ruin.
That is the will of Dark Tiger.

158
00:09:45,583 --> 00:09:49,291
And whatever our master decrees,
we will see done without fail.

159
00:09:54,125 --> 00:09:56,958
[evil chuckling]

160
00:09:58,541 --> 00:10:00,041
[YUUKI]
I’m sure you’re confused,

161
00:10:00,125 --> 00:10:03,000
but there’s a reason I left
this inheritance to you.

162
00:10:03,083 --> 00:10:06,041
I want you to use this money
to protect my dear Rei,

163
00:10:06,125 --> 00:10:09,916
and ensure that the two of you
live happily ever after.

164
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:11,083
[gasps]

165
00:10:11,166 --> 00:10:12,083
[yelps]

166
00:10:12,166 --> 00:10:14,333
♪

167
00:10:22,208 --> 00:10:25,833
I didn’t think it was possible
to be this happy!

168
00:10:26,833 --> 00:10:29,416
Oh, stop, Rei!
What would Grandfather think?

169
00:10:29,500 --> 00:10:31,416
On second thought,
my body is ready!

170
00:10:31,500 --> 00:10:33,666
My body is so rea--

171
00:10:33,750 --> 00:10:35,458
[YUUKI]
One more thing.

172
00:10:35,541 --> 00:10:38,916
Rei and I are not
biologically related.

173
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:41,250
Her actual mother and father

174
00:10:41,333 --> 00:10:44,333
were brutally murdered
by the enemy.

175
00:10:44,416 --> 00:10:47,208
Her parents were
dear friends of mine.

176
00:10:47,291 --> 00:10:50,166
Comrades, with a similar purpose
and iron resolve.

177
00:10:51,125 --> 00:10:53,666
But the enemy got to them,
and eliminated them...

178
00:10:54,875 --> 00:10:58,291
leaving Rei alone
without a guardian.

179
00:11:02,333 --> 00:11:05,250
[YUUKI]
That day, I became her father.

180
00:11:05,333 --> 00:11:09,541
I did what I could to raise her
and keep her out of harm’s way.

181
00:11:09,625 --> 00:11:11,583
[SUIGIN]
Grandfather.

182
00:11:11,666 --> 00:11:13,333
[REI]
Stop, please!

183
00:11:13,416 --> 00:11:14,708
[MAN]
Not our fault.

184
00:11:14,791 --> 00:11:17,166
Blame your old man
for leaving you this mess.

185
00:11:17,250 --> 00:11:19,833
[REI] My father would never
have left that much debt!

186
00:11:19,916 --> 00:11:21,458
Let go of me!

187
00:11:21,541 --> 00:11:24,083
[MAN] Tell us your sob story
back at the office.

188
00:11:24,166 --> 00:11:25,208
[REI]
I’m not going anywhere!

189
00:11:25,291 --> 00:11:26,333
Stop struggling!

190
00:11:27,291 --> 00:11:28,666
Bastards!

191
00:11:28,750 --> 00:11:29,708
[grunts]

192
00:11:30,833 --> 00:11:33,958
[YUUKI] Suigin.
Use this inheritance well.

193
00:11:34,041 --> 00:11:37,250
Now you are the only one
who can protect Rei.

194
00:11:37,333 --> 00:11:38,541
Hold it!

195
00:11:38,625 --> 00:11:39,875
Who's this?

196
00:11:39,958 --> 00:11:41,708
Let her go.

197
00:11:41,791 --> 00:11:43,125
Right now!

198
00:13:15,208 --> 00:13:17,416
[SUIGIN]
The Silver Guardian

